works.complaint:
It is illegal for the sites above to have published  
content about me including private images. Having spoken to a legal  
advisor, I am aware that the written content and the published stolen  
images clearly qualify as defamation of character. The above material also
 
clearly violates my basic human right to privacy.
The sites feel that they can keep this material visible because they know 

that I would need to pay for an injunction to remove it, which as a young 

person, I cannot afford. I have suffered for five years as a result of  
these images on the internet. These two sites now appear to be the only  
remaining publishers of them. Their continued persecution is wrong and  
illegal. I would therefore like your help in removing the URL's from your 

search results. This would change my life significantly for the better.
